post_content.caption: Disgraced former FTX CEO Sam Bankman-Fried sentenced to 25 years for financial fraud
post_content.description:
A judge sentenced Sam Bankman-Fried to 25 years in prison for orchestrating what prosecutors have called one of the biggest financial frauds in American history.
